OL,4,CDad's plea for answers over child's
OL,5,Chospital death
OL,6, A father whose child died at a mental
OL,7, health hospital where a culture of
OL,8, abuse was uncovered has told of his
OL,9, hopes for answers from an inquest.
OL,11,FRowan Thompson, 18, was one of three
OL,12,Fpeople who died over a nine-month
OL,13,Fperiod at a unit at Prestwich Hospital
OL,14,Fin Greater Manchester.
OL,16,FThe BBC's Panorama programme found a
OL,17,F"toxic culture" of "bullying" at
OL,18,Fanother unit at the same hospital.
OL,20,FMarc Thompson said he needed "an answer
OL,21,Fto the question how my child died."
